Lynn.HitchcockA MATRIC pupil from Sidakeni village outside Matatiele, Chwayita Sitshetshe (22), is devastated after her two-year- old son went missing on 8 September. She leaves her child with her mother when she goes to school. My mother left the child with my neighbour and when she returned home the child was missing, said Sitshetshe.Anyone with information should contact Lukholweni police station on 039 257 3012 or her mother Sitshetshe on 072 787 9440. - Supplied.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.